# Terms of Service for RKL Assistant

Effective Date: 4/2/2025

## 1. Acceptance of Terms

By inviting, using, or accessing RKL Assistant (the "Bot") on Discord, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms of Service (the "Terms"). If you do not agree with any of these terms, you must not use the Bot.

## 2. Description of the Bot

RKL Assistant is a Discord bot that provides assistance for RKL adminstrators to manage their clan. The Bot interacts with the Discord platform and users via commands and permissions.

## 3. Usage Guidelines

- You may use the Bot in any Discord server that you have administrative privileges for, and only in compliance with Discord’s terms of service.
- You agree not to use the Bot for any unlawful, harmful, abusive, or malicious activities, including but not limited to:
- Spamming or flooding Discord servers.
- Using the Bot to harass, bully, or otherwise harm other users.
- Attempting to exploit the Bot for malicious purposes (e.g., hacking, phishing).
- Violating the privacy of other users.

## 4. Permissions and Access

- The Bot requires specific permissions to operate effectively in Discord servers, such as reading and sending messages, managing roles, or connecting to voice channels (if applicable). These permissions are granted by the server administrator when the Bot is invited.
- The Bot may collect certain data, such as server ID, user ID, and command usage statistics, to improve functionality and support. However, no sensitive personal data will be collected or stored without your explicit consent.

## 5. Data Collection

- RKL Assistant may collect and process information related to its use, including but not limited to Discord user IDs, command logs, and server statistics. This data may be used to improve the Bot’s performance and features.
- No personal data (e.g., email, IP addresses) will be intentionally collected or stored. Any data that may be considered personally identifiable will only be collected if absolutely necessary for the Bot's functionality.

## 6. Updates and Maintenance

- The Bot may undergo periodic updates, improvements, or maintenance. While we strive to keep the Bot running smoothly, there may be times when it experiences downtime or bugs. We are not responsible for any downtime or disruptions caused by these updates.
- The Bot's functionality may change over time, and we reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate any feature without prior notice.

## 7. Termination

- You or the administrator of any server using the Bot may stop using the Bot at any time by removing or disabling it in the server.
- We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access to the Bot for any user or server that violates these Terms of Service or engages in prohibited conduct.

## 8. Limitation of Liability

To the extent permitted by law, RKL Assistant and its developers shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use of the Bot, including but not limited to loss of data, server downtime, or personal damage.

## 9. Indemnification

You agree to indemnify and hold harmless RKL Assistant, its developers, and Discord from any claims, damages, or losses arising from your use of the Bot, including but not limited to violations of these Terms of Service.

## 10. Changes to the Terms

We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Any changes will be posted in this document with an updated "Effective Date." Continued use of the Bot after such changes will constitute your acceptance of the updated Terms.

## 11. Governing Law

These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the competent courts of the United States.

